We may collect various pieces of information if you seek to place an order for a product with us on the Platform.
We collect, store and process the data that you provide for processing your purchase on the Platform and any possible later claims, and to provide you with our services. We may collect personal information including, but not limited to, title, name, gender, date of birth, Computerized National Identity Card details, email address, postal address, delivery address (if different), telephone number, mobile number, fax number, payment details, payment card details or bank account details.
